        <abstract> 
<p>Sends subscription for the <hi rend="italic">Index</hi>.</p>  
<p>FEA’s article ["The intuitional and scientific schools of free religion", <hi rend="italic">Index</hi> 15 Apr 1871] is one of the most striking CD has read.</p> 
        </abstract>
